data.name: grdOCS0201.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT NVL(A.MEMB , ' ') MEMB, NVL(A.SEQ , 0 ) SEQ, NVL(A.DISPLAY_YN , 'N') DISPLAY_YN, NVL(A.SLIP_GUBUN , ' ') SLIP_GUBUN, NVL(B.SLIP_GUBUN_NAME, ' ') SLIP_GUBUN_NAME, DECODE(NVL(A.DISPLAY_YN, 'N'), 'Y', ' ', 'N', '') "SELECT" FROM OCS0201 A, OCS0101 B WHERE A.MEMB = :f_memb AND A.SLIP_GUBUN = B.SLIP_GUBUN UNION ALL SELECT :f_memb MEMB, 0 SEQ, 'N' DISPLAY_YN, NVL(A.SLIP_GUBUN , ' ') SLIP_GUBUN, NVL(A.SLIP_GUBUN_NAME, ' ') SLIP_GUBUN_NAME, '' "SELECT" FROM OCS0101 A WHERE NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM OCS0201 B WHERE B.MEMB = :f_memb AND B.SLIP_GUBUN = A.SLIP_GUBUN ) ORDER BY 4

data.name: grdOCS0202.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.MEMB , A.SLIP_GUBUN, A.SEQ , NVL(A.DISPLAY_YN, 'N'), A.SLIP_CODE , B.SLIP_NAME , DECODE(NVL(A.DISPLAY_YN, 'N'), 'Y', ' ', 'N', '') "SELECT" FROM OCS0202 A, OCS0102 B WHERE A.MEMB = :f_memb AND A.SLIP_GUBUN = :f_slip_gubun AND B.SLIP_GUBUN = A.SLIP_GUBUN AND B.SLIP_CODE = A.SLIP_CODE UNION ALL SELECT :f_memb MEMB , A.SLIP_GUBUN SLIP_GUBUN, 0 SEQ , 'N' DISPLAY_YN, A.SLIP_CODE , A.SLIP_NAME , '' "SELECT" FROM OCS0102 A WHERE A.SLIP_GUBUN = :f_slip_gubun AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM OCS0202 B WHERE B.MEMB = :f_memb AND B.SLIP_GUBUN = A.SLIP_GUBUN AND B.SLIP_CODE = A.SLIP_CODE ) ORDER BY 5
